    "name": "Color",
    "handle": "color",
    "description": "Defines the primary color or pattern, such as blue or striped"
  },
  "notes": [
    "Shopify standard taxonomy uses 19 canonical color values for the generic Color attribute.",
    "Identifiers are stable global IDs (gid://shopify/TaxonomyValue/<n>) plus URL-safe handles (color__<slug>).",
    "Hex codes are NOT part of the standard taxonomy — they must be supplied per-merchant via metaobjects, theme settings, or category metafield swatch UI.",
    "Hex codes below are aimily's editorial defaults (typical CSS named-color or visually-representative tone) for reference UI only — not authoritative.",
    "Beauty industries get richer dedicated palettes (hair-color-shade: 34 values, makeup-color-shade: 30 values). Apparel/footwear inherits the 19 generic values."
  ],
